commit message: Update F-Droid badge
Polish translation
Change a view id that was sometimes causing conflicts
Move UriLauncherActivity to ui package and delete UrlMatcher
Only open links if we find an exact match for the intent
When we can't open a link, try to open it in a browser

Improve support for user and organization URLs

New supported URLs:
https://github.com/stars/jonan
https://github.com/jonan/followers
https://github.com/jonan/following
https://github.com/orgs/github
https://github.com/orgs/github/people
https://github.com/orgs/github/teams
Add tests for the new supported URLs
Update changelog
Improve how GitHub links are opened
Upgrade Android Gradle plugin
Remove all low-res icons
Use Material Design icons in the toolbar
Show who changed the assignee of an issue

Improve support for commit and commit compare URLs

New supported URLs:
https://github.com/jonan/ForkHub/commit/branch
https://github.com/jonan/ForkHub/compare/branch
https://github.com/jonan/ForkHub/compare/branch1...branch2
Fix crash when a pull request has a null base
Center icons in PR information verticaly

Revamped search interface to use the support library SearchView

Closes #166
Minor improvement to the headers creation of the repositories tab
Move call inside if statement
Update User-Agent
Show review events in pull requests
Update changelog
ForkHub v1.2.1
